OL,3,CWords matter: How to talk about suicide
OL,5,FJudd Skelton, the chair of Greater
OL,6,FManchester Suicide Prevention,
OL,7,Fexplains to ITV Granda Reports
OL,8,Fpresenter Victoria Grimes why language
OL,9,Fis so important when we talk about
OL,10,Fsuicide.
OL,12,FWhen it comes to suicide, words matter.
OL,14,FIf you are worried about a friend,
OL,15,Fcolleague or loved one, it can be
OL,16,Freally hard to know how you can help
OL,17,Fin a respectful and meaningful way.
