OL,3,CWords matter: How to talk about suicide
OL,5,FThat is why learning how to talk about
OL,6,Fsuicide has the power to save lives,
OL,7,Faccording to the Greater Manchester
OL,8,Fcharity Shining A Light on Suicide.
OL,10,FSuicidal thoughts may come and then
OL,11,Fdisappear for some people, others
OL,12,Fmight experience them for years or
OL,13,Fhave feelings bubble up in response to
OL,14,Fchanging moods or life events.
OL,16,FShould suicide prevention be taught in
OL,17,Fschools? We ask the question in our
OL,18,Fpodcast, From the North
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
