OL,3,CWords matter: How to talk about suicide
OL,5,FAccording to Shining A Light, the best
OL,6,Fthing you can do is to ask them
OL,7,Fdirectly and give them the opportunity
OL,8,Fto tell you how they are feeling.
OL,10,FBut it is not always easy as we still
OL,11,Flive in a society which can still
OL,12,Ftreat suicide as a taboo, says Judd
OL,13,FSkelton, the chair of Greater
OL,14,FManchester Suicide Prevention.
OL,16,F"We need to get to a place where we're
OL,17,Fusing language that isn't judgemental
OL,18,Fand supports positive conversations,"
OL,19,FJudd said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
