OL,3,CWords matter: How to talk about suicide
OL,5,FSuicide Harbours, run by EPiC HOPE,
OL,6,Fare also available across the North
OL,7,FWest, including The Crisis Harbour in
OL,8,FAtherton, Greater Manchester, which
OL,9,Faims to cut down on A&E admissions for
OL,10,Fthose in crisis.
OL,12,FThe centre is a drop in location for
OL,13,Fpeople who are struggling and in need
OL,14,Fof a safe space to go to when they are
OL,15,Ffeeling trapped, overwhelmed or
OL,16,Fhelpless.
OL,18,FJust one month from opening, it helped
OL,19,Fsave the lives of 17 people.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
