OL,3,CWords matter: How to talk about suicide
OL,5,F"We know that asking people if they've
OL,6,Fhad suicidal thoughts doesn't put the
OL,7,Fidea in people's heads.
OL,9,F"If people haven't had suicidal
OL,10,Fthoughts they'll tell you, and if they
OL,11,Fhave, they'll feel like you've opened
OL,12,Fup a conversation that they've felt
OL,13,Fmight be closed down in other places.
OL,15,F"It is really important that we speak
OL,16,Fto people who have had this lived
OL,17,Fexperience and ask 'what would have
OL,18,Fhelped you then and what would help
OL,19,Fyou now?'"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
